pment. Our results also demonstrate that simple, inexpensive, battery-\u00adoperated homemade air samplers can collect an abundance of eDNA from the air, opening the opportunity for sampling in remote environments.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Garrett, Nina R.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Watkins, Jonathan", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Simmons, Nancy B.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Fenton, Brock", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Maeda\u2010Obregon, Alejandro", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Sanchez, Daniel E.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Froehlich, Emma M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Walker, Faith M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Littlefair, Joanne E.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Clare, Elizabeth L.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/a3b1190a7b5efe7311215832adc11c58", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/7f02ca7cc43bf976b39860af108a78d1e7b1847681dc55cc2b14ff14a520a015", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/YNPKVU3G", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/YNPKVU3G", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/00cb5111715f362de0c7507333682ab3!/b211850-214317", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "2", "p